    <td class="roweven" valign="top" width="2000">Since vim 7.0 supports :smap (mappings that apply only to Select mode) I updated the script to use these.&nbsp;&nbsp;Now the maps defined by the script for when completion is active will not do anything unexpected in Visual mode.<br><br>I also updated the installation instructions in the comments at the top of the file.</td>
</tr>
