    <td class="rowodd" valign="top"><i><a href="/account/profile.php?user_id=92">Benji Fisher</a></i></td>
    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" width="2000">I added a configuration section.&nbsp;&nbsp;You can now change<br>(1) a minimum length of word to be completed<br>(2) the character (default &lt;Tab&gt;) used to accept the completion.<br><br>I also added some comments and separated a StartAppend() function (which is called twice).</td>
</tr>
